  by
  refine' real.is_topological_basis_Ioo_rat.dense_iff.2 _
  simp only [mem_Union, mem_singleton_iff]
  rintro _ ⟨a, b, hlt, rfl⟩ hne; rw [inter_comm]
  exact exists_irrational_btwn (Rat.cast_lt.2 hlt)
